                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8085" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1258</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13599 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浴火涅槃，危后逢生：造假风波后瑞幸咖啡的自我觉醒之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Rise from the ashes, after danger comes life:Luckin Coffee&#39;s road to self-awakening after the fraud scandal</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘李福，孟禹衡（通讯作者），王岩，祖榕，李本春</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">瑞幸咖啡股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务造假；财务合规；财务管理；战略管理会计；公司治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Financial fraud, financial compliance, financial management, strategic management accounting, corporate governance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020年，瑞幸因财务造假事件折戟退市，这一事件在中美资本市场引起了广泛的关注。然而，跌入谷底的瑞幸通过一系列的改革措施，走出了一条堪称经典的自我觉醒之路。案例基于中美资本市场制度的差异，对瑞幸财务舞弊事件进行系统分析，从财务管理、战略管理会计和公司治理三方面探讨财务造假风波后的瑞幸如何进行自我革命，以达“触底反弹”之效。案例旨在引导学员认识到财务造假对企业的破坏性影响，从而强化财务管理、公司战略和风险管控等层面的实践能力。通过分析瑞幸的自我革命过程，学员可以了解到财务合规的重要性以及企业恢复与重建的路径和策略。同时，案例分析有助于学员对中美资本市场制度差异的理解，以及在跨国经营中如何应对财务风险和强化公司治理的思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2020, Luckin Coffee fell and delisted due to a financial fraud scandal, which drew widespread attention in both the Chinese and American capital markets. However, from rock bottom, Luckin embarked on a remarkable journey of self-awakening through a series of reform measures. This case study provides a systematic analysis of the Luckin financial fraud incident based on the differences in the capital market systems between China and the United States. It explores how Luckin underwent self-revolution in financial management, strategic management accounting, and corporate governance, achieving a “bounce back” effect. The aim of this case study is to guide students to recognize the destructive impact of financial fraud on companies, thereby strengthening their practical abilities in financial management, corporate strategy, and risk control. By analyzing Luckin’s process of self-revolution, students can understand the importance of financial compliance and the path and strategies for corporate recovery and rebuilding. Additionally, the case analysis helps students understand the differences in the capital market systems between China and the United States, and encourages them to explore how to cope with financial risks and strengthen corporate governance in cross-border operations.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》、《管理会计》、《公司战略与风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中概股的内涵，以及新《公司法》、新《票据法》规范下的中概股退市机制及其实现途径、风险应对；会计核算与财务舞弊的内涵，财务会计核算的基本原则和程序，财务舞弊实现的主要手段和重要影响；财务管理的内涵，财务管理的基本目标、主要活动及内在相关性；战略管理的基本内涵，战略管理会计与财务会计的内在关联性；公司治理的内涵，完善公司治理机制和利益相关者保护机制的基础、举措</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
